            <title>[LU-9337] LBUG replay-single test_0b: test failed to respond and timed out</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9337</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/8baa7d07-fb21-464b-b398-6efd6998da7d&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/8baa7d07-fb21-464b-b398-6efd6998da7d&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks similar to closed ticket &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5425&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite conf-sanity, subtest test_32a (mount OST failed)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5425&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5425&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From MDS console:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Lustre: MGS: haven&apos;t heard from client 3730229d-e6d4-a78a-d7f3-f175c56b9449 (at 10.2.4.109@tcp) in 50 seconds. I think it&apos;s dead, and I am evicting it.
LustreError: 7759:0:(osp_sync.c:345:osp_sync_declare_add()) ASSERTION( ctxt ) failed: 
LustreError: 7759:0:(osp_sync.c:345:osp_sync_declare_add()) LBUG 
Kernel panic - not syncing: LBUG
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From OST dmesg:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;LustreError: 8237:0:(osd_handler.c:6856:osd_mount()) lustre-OST0000-osd: can&apos;t mount /dev/mapper/lvm--Role_OSS-P1: -22
LustreError: 8237:0:(obd_config.c:574:class_setup()) setup lustre-OST0000-osd failed (-22)
LustreError: 8237:0:(obd_mount.c:199:lustre_start_simple()) lustre-OST0000-osd setup error -22
LustreError: 8237:0:(obd_mount_server.c:1806:server_fill_super()) Unable to start osd on /dev/mapper/lvm--Role_OSS-P1: -22
LustreError: 8237:0:(obd_mount.c:1502:lustre_fill_super()) Unable to mount  (-22)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
